# Poppy Pots — Cursor rules

## General

- Changed-code-only: edit only files required by the task
- Stay in scope: no unrequested features, dependencies, or files
- Ask, don't assume: clarify ambiguous requirements before building
- Simplest solution first: smallest correct diff, no premature abstraction
- End responses with FILES CHANGED / NOT TOUCHED / CONCERNS summary

## Project invariants

- Demo site is a single file: site/index.html (no splitting unless asked)
- Route all colors through CSS custom properties (var(--pp-*))
- Catalog data lives in PRODUCTS, COLORS, ART objects in index.html
- SKU pattern: PP-{SIZE}-{COLOR}-{PATTERN}
- Free shipping threshold $75 — sync site/index.html FREE_SHIPPING_THRESHOLD and shopify/snippets/pp-free-shipping-bar.liquid pp_free_shipping_threshold
- Demo checkout is a modal only — never wire real payments into the demo

## Adding a product

1. Add to PRODUCTS (and COLORS/ART if needed) in site/index.html
2. Add variant rows to shopify/poppy-pots-products.csv following SKU pattern
3. Verify in browser and against CSV

## Key files

- site/index.html — demo storefront
- shopify/poppy-pots-products.csv — Shopify product import
- shopify/snippets/pp-free-shipping-bar.liquid — shipping bar
- shopify/sections/pp-marquee.liquid — scrolling banner
- README.md — architecture and design tokens
- AGENTS.md — full dev conventions
